 <item> <title>Education Department Invites Districts to Apply for $400 Million Race to the Top Competition to Support Classroom-Level Reform Efforts</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/education-department-invites-districts-apply-400-million-race-top-competition-support-classroom-level-reform-efforts</link>
